 retry but produced typecheck errors in the report, suggesting the retry may have passed without properly resolving the underlying TypeScript type mismatches in PagesPageConfig validation. | Failed at: ship | Suggestion: Add a `git fetch origin main` step before the ship stage's force-push to ensure the local ref is up-to-date with remote, and investigate whether the verify stage's retry logic is properly re-running type checks rather than passing cached results. | Flaw: ship — Git push rejected due to stale remote ref — no fetch/update before push | Stages: taskify:completed, plan:completed, build:completed, verify:completed, review:completed, review-fix:completed, ship:failed","createdAt":"2026-04-10T16:17:53.227Z","wordCount":963,"positions":[0,7,14,21,29,34,50,59,68,85,94,108,115,122,134,144,148,153,160,166,173,181,189,197,205,210,221,234,247,254,260,270,278,288,297,307,321,329,344,359,366,374,383,397,408,419,424,438,454,468,479,486,498,505,509,515,522,528,533,544,549,557,563,571,582,588,595,601,611,623,635,647,654,662,668,677,686,689,697,702,709,716,721,729,736,747,753,760,764,769,778,785,791,798,804,807,813,820,827,834,842,850,861,866,877,883,894,901,912,919,930,937,941,952,957]},"ep_stage_diary_001":{"taskId":"decompose-2781-260418-164536","episodeId":"ep_stage_diary_001","source":"stage_diary","content":"{\"stage\":\"build\",\"insights\":[{\"kind\":\"convention\",\"text\":\"Utility modules follow a typed Options interface pattern (e.g., debounce, retry, configValidator) with named exports and JSDoc comments.\",\"scope\":\"src/utils\"},{\"kind\":\"convention\",\"text\":\"Use Result<T, E> discriminated union (Ok/Err) from src/utils/result.ts for explicit error handling instead of throwing.\",\"scope\":\"src/utils/result.ts\"},{\"kind\":\"convention\",\"text\":\"Tests co-located next to source (configValidator.test.ts beside configValidator.ts), using describe/it blocks, vi.fn(), and beforeEach/afterEach for cleanup.\",\"scope\":\"testing\"},{\"kind\":\"lesson\